://pixelplex.io/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/bitnetwork-slide-3-1600.jpg","alt":"News and currency exchange key metrics screens of Bitnetwork platform"},"image_768":"https://pixelplex.io/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/bitnetwork-slide-3-768.jpg","image_500":"https://pixelplex.io/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/bitnetwork-slide-3-500.jpg","image_320":"https://pixelplex.io/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/bitnetwork-slide-3-320.jpg"}],"rows":[{"title":"","text":"<p>The industry was facing various problems, including the following:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Most <a href=\"https://pixelplex.io/cryptocurrency-exchange-development/\">crypto exchanges</a> lacked in security</li>\n<li>Frequent cases of fraud were damaging the credibility of crypto exchanges</li>\n<li>High fees did not allow brokers to benefit from trading</li>\n<li>Unethical response time from exchange support teams on vital issues, such as account suspension and 2FA</li>\n<li>Difficulties in obtaining withdrawal and deposit information</li>\n</ul>\n<p>The platform&#8217;s web and <a href=\"https://pixelplex.io/mobile-app-development/\">mobile apps</a> have customizable trading UI templates allowing the user to pull out and set up the trading modules they need in a format that is convenient for them.</p>\n<p>Over 20 trading modules are customizable as well, so the user can individually configure each module by style and display. The minimal trading module set provides simple UI for trading processes. Trading modules include candle chart, visual depth, order book, trading logs, ticker display, and others.</p>\n<p>To ensure security, we have included three types of 2-factor authorization. To start bidding, users have to enter personal data and pass verification. This type of authorization process is highly secure.</p>\n<p>To enable timely communication with users we&#8217;ve included a chat feature, as well as a ticket system for customer support.</p>\n<p>The admin section includes viewing reports, setting fees and user management features.</p>\n"}],"title":"Details"},{"acf_fc_layout":"call_to_action","title":"Got an idea? Let’s work together","button_text":"Get in touch","background_rgb":"#64C7B4"},{"acf_fc_layout":"projectFeatures","title":"Project features","content":[{"title":"Support for two types of orders: limit and market","image":{"url":"https://pixelplex.io/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/Support-for-two-types-of-orders_-limit-and-market.svg","alt":"Blue icon of two divided documents"}},{"title":"Over 20 trading modules","image":{"url":"https://pixelplex.io/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/Over-20-trading-modules.svg","alt":"Blue icon of three blocks connected by two arrows"}},{"title":"18 trading pairs","image":{"url":"https://pixelplex.io/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/18-trading-pairs.svg","alt":"Blue icon of two dashboards"}},{"title":"Three types of 2FA: via Google authenticator, email and SMS","image":{"url":"https://pixelplex.io/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/Three-types-of-2FA_-via-Google-authenticator-email-and-SMS.svg","alt":"Blue icon of a human and a password line"}},{"title":"Live chat and ticket system customer support","image":{"url":"https://pixelplex.io/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/Live-chat-and-ticket-system-customer-support.svg","alt":"Blue icon of a human and two chat clouds"}}]},{"acf_fc_layout":"relatedPosts","project":[1341,2058]}],"seoTitle":"Bitnetwork - Crypto Exchange for Professional Traders | PixelPlex","seoDescription":"Web and mobile cryptocurrency exchange for professional traders with over 20 customizable modules, high level of security, customer service and support","seoKeywords":""},"category":"","officesLocations":[{"id":86,"name":"New York, United States","city":"New York","country":"United States","address":[{"entry":"520 West 28th St."},{"entry":"Suite 31"},{"entry":"New York, NY 10001"}],"phone":{"raw":"+16464900772","formatted":"+1 646 490 0772"},"order":"1"},{"id":7479,"name":"London, United Kingdom","city":"London","country":"United Kingdom","address":[{"entry":"Kem